======================================
Not only lives but also each and every stuff are in state of interaction. The reason for interaction is for their stability.
If lives realize it get energy form another lives for their stability then they try to perceive towards interaction with them.
If objects/energies realize it get energy for their stability from another objects/energies then they perceive towards interaction.

Interaction of objects/energies/lives are always is in state of streaming, ie it is in auto action or perceive towards the action.

If fact not the lives but the state of energy inside life interact to another state of lives since these states try to stabilize by use of anthers energy.

One important thing can be notice here, Before interaction of energies/objects between them they both are in some what similar states/frequencies.
If one state of energy is at very lower state then this energy can,t interact to higher state of energy, in fact lower state of energy unable to detect the higher state of energy even higher state of energy always in front of lower state of energy.

***Every thing always in front of us in different state of energy/frequencies but we are able to detect only similar frequencies of energy where our state exists***

Ex-
-We can't detect the mobile wave/energy, it will detect by arrangement of waves in mobile only.
-We can read spiritual book but since it had been written by very high state of energy, we can't detect the waves injected into them.
-We a simple person can purpose a heroine since both have different state of energy/understanding, even one purpose higher state will take lightly.
-One lives of male can't interact another life of female since both are in different states.
so on.

The sates in which two/more than two energy/ lives/ object/ waves..so on interact each others when they are in co state.

***Co state is almost common state of emerges/waves when they get interacted***

-Ear are in state of lighten some particular range of sound frequencies beyond that limit our ear unable to detect the waves of sounds.

-When energy in us are in the sate of senses/mind then we can detect the object for our use.
-When we are in sate of observation then we detect their behavior/inner arrangement of the same object.
-When we are in state of realization/streaming then we can detect the waves flying inside same object.

Ie..Objects/energy/waves always are in front of us every time but when our state get changed we realize/observe the same thing in different manor.
In fact not we but the sate of energy in us and their frequencies interact the object/frequency when they are in co state.

***one can change their state by continuous supply of energy***
